title: NextEra Energy and Google enter new partnership to accelerate AI growth and develop data centers
description: NextEra Energy and Google Cloud are expanding their collaboration to develop gigawatt-scale data center campuses in the U.S., aiming for rapid growth and enhanced AI capabilities by mid-2026.
